The file is converted from allegro_hand_description_right.xacro from the ROS package of Allegro Hand (https://github.com/felixduvallet/allegro-hand-ros/tree/master/allegro_hand_description). The model files (.obj files and .mtl files) are converted from the .STL files from the same source. Some modifications on the model are made according to the physical common knowledge - the damping values of the joints are minimized for about 300 times based on the original value. The inertia of all the parts are re-measured using Meshlab and the provided mass. The collision of link_13 is deleted in this version of file because it frequently cases unnecessary collsiions. 
 =================================================================================== -->
